prerequisites:
be cheap and not want to spend cash on external solutions
file server pre-configured
domain controller
some storage disks
-----------------------
enter server manager
go to file and storage services
create new storage pool
specify name for pool
select disks
leave the disks on 'automatic' and configure later if you want
create
right click the storage space, create storage pool virtual disk
first pool is always primordial
name new virtual disk
assign storage tiers among the disks if disks are disparate
select raid model
create
create a volume from new storage pool virtual disk
allocate entire size
assign drive letter
select filesystem
assign volume label
create
done
